  "prompt": "Which is best IT institute in Delhi?",
  "response": "Choosing the best IT institute in Delhi depends on various factors such as the specific courses you're interested in, the faculty, placement records, infrastructure, and your budget. However, some of the well-regarded IT institutes in Delhi include:\n\n1. **Indian Institute of Technology Delhi (IIT Delhi)** - Offers advanced courses and is highly respected for its engineering programs.\n\n2. **Delhi Technological University (DTU)** - Known for its engineering courses and has a good reputation in the IT sector.\n\n3. **Institute of Information Technology and Management (IITM)** - Offers various IT-related courses and has a decent placement record.\n\n4. **NIIT** - Known for professional training in IT and offers various certification courses.\n\n5. **Aptech** - Offers a range of IT courses and has a network of centers across the country.\n\n6. **Jetking** - Focuses on networking and hardware courses and is well-known in that niche.\n\n7. **TCS iON Digital Learning Hub** - Offers a range of IT courses with a focus on practical skills.\n\n8. **Amity University** - Offers comprehensive IT programs with good facilities and placements.\n\nBefore making a decision, it's advisable to research the specific programs offered, visit campuses if possible, and read reviews from current or former students.",
